Package: ggsegSUIT
Title: SUIT Cerebellar Lobular Atlas for the 'ggseg' Ecosystem
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Athanasia Mo", "Mowinckel", , "a.m.mowinckel@psykologi.uio.no", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-5756-0223"))
  )
Description: SUIT cerebellar parcellation into anatomical lobules and deep
    nuclei for the 'ggseg' ecosystem. Provides a unified 'ggseg_atlas' object
    with both 2D polygon geometry and 3D vertex indices, for use with 'ggseg'
    and 'ggseg3d'.
